      <div class="prose sm:prose-lg prose-zinc text-center mx-auto my-6 dark:prose-invert">
        <p>Transparent and hassle-free pricing that aligns with your real estate investment goals. No hidden fees, just clarity and value.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-6 group mx-auto max-w-5xl flex-wrap">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white p-1 border border-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:border-zinc-600/80">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" data-action="click->pricing#toggle"
            data-pricing-target="intervalBtn">Monthly</button>
          <button class="btn btn-transparent" data-action="click->pricing#toggle"
            data-pricing-target="intervalBtn">Annual</button>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full pt-6 hidden" data-pricing-target="promotion">
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-primary-50 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-primary-600 dark:bg-primary-500/10 dark:text-primary-400">Get <span class="font-semibold">2 months free</span> with annual plans!</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start">
  <div class="lg:w-1/3 w-full lg:pr-6 lg:mb-0 mb-10">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white border-zinc-300 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:border-zinc-600/80 border p-6 shadow">
      <h3 class="h5 text-secondary-500 mt-3">Freelancer</h3>
      <p class="font-extrabold text-4xl tracking my-2 tight">
        <span data-pricing-target="price" data-month="$29" data-year="$290" class="dark:text-white">$29</span>
        <span class="font-normal text-sm text-zinc-600 tracking-normal dark:text-zinc-200"
            data-pricing-target="interval">/month</span>
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert">
        <p>The essentials to get you started.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-6 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <% [
            { item: "Advanced revenue management" },
            { item: "Multi-property portfolio management" },
            { item: "Dedicated account manager" },
            { item: "Custom integrations and API access" },
            { item: "Priority customer support" }
            ].each do |pricing| %>
          <li class="flex items-center py-3 gap-2">
            <%= icon "check", class: "size-5 text-secondary-500 flex-shrink-0", variant: :solid %>
            <p class="leading-tight"><%= pricing[:item] %></p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>

      <%= link_to "Get Started", "#", class: "btn btn-secondary w-full mt-6 text-center" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="lg:w-1/3 lg:px-3 w-full lg:mb-0 mb-10">
    <div
        class="rounded-3xl bg-white border-zinc-300 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:border-zinc-600/80 border p-6 shadow relative">
      <div class="bg-primary-500 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-white absolute -top-4 text-sm font-semibold left-4">Most
        popular</div>
      <h3 class="h5 text-primary-500 mt-3">Professional</h3>
      <p class="font-extrabold text-4xl tracking my-2 tight">
        <span data-pricing-target="price" data-month="$99" data-year="$990" class="dark:text-white">$99</span>
        <span class="font-normal text-sm text-zinc-600 tracking-normal dark:text-zinc-200"
            data-pricing-target="interval">/month</span>
      </p>
      <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert">
        <p>The plan that packs a punch without breaking the bank.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-6 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <% [
            { item: "AI-powered pricing optimization" },
            { item: "Real-time market analysis" },
            { item: "Automated booking management" },
            { item: "Customizable property listings" },
            { item: "Guest communication tools" },
            { item: "Performance analytics dashboard" }
            ].each do |pricing| %>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 py-3">
            <%= icon "check", class: "size-5 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0", variant: :solid %>

            <p class="leading-tight"><%= pricing[:item] %></p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>

      <%= link_to "Get Started", "#", class: "btn btn-primary w-full mt-6 text-center" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="lg:w-1/3 w-full lg:pl-6 lg:mb-0 mb-10">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border-zinc-300 border p-6 shadow-sm dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:border-zinc-600/80 relative">
      <h3 class="h5 text-zinc-800 my-3 dark:text-zinc-200">Enterprise</h3>
      <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert">
        <p>A tailored plan for more control.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-6 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <% [
            { item: "AI-powered pricing optimization" },
            { item: "Real-time market analysis" },
            { item: "Automated booking management" },
            { item: "Customizable property listings" },
            { item: "Guest communication tools" },
            { item: "Performance analytics dashboard" },
            { item: "Revenue forecasting" },
            { item: "Seasonal demand predictions" },
            { item: "Integration with major booking platforms" },
            ].each do |pricing| %>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 py-3">
            <%= icon "check", class: "size-5 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-500 flex-shrink-0", variant: :solid %>

            <p class="leading-tight"><%= pricing[:item] %></p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>

      <%= link_to "Get Started", "#", class: "btn btn-dark dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:hover:bg-zinc-950 w-full mt-6 text-center" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-primary-500 dark:bg-zinc-800 min-h-[300px] relative mt-20 flex justify-center items-center px-4">
  <div class="bg-cover inset-0 absolute w-full h-full z-10 mix-blend-multiply bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_url('railsui/faq.png') %>);"></div>
  <div class="relative z-50 text-center">
    <h3 class="md:h2 h3 !text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert text-white mt-6">Looking to get answers faster? Explore our comprehensive list of frequently asked questions to find quick solutions and insights about Shepherd.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-10 px-4">
  <% [
      {
        q: "What does Shepherd do?",
        a: "Shepherd leverages AI to empower real estate investors, helping them maximize income from vacation rentals."
      },
      {
        q: "How does Shepherd use AI in real estate investment?",
        a: "Our AI-driven solutions optimize vacation rental performance, ensuring that investors get the most out of their properties."
      },
      {
        q: "Why is optimization important for vacation rentals?",
        a: "With vacation rentals, money is oftet left on the table if not optimized. Shepherd ensures that investors don't miss out on potential income."
      },
      {
        q: "What makes Shepherd's solutions unique?",
        a: "We provide investors with greater control over their earnings. Our products offer insights and tools that allow investors to actively shape their financial outcomes."
      },
      {
        q: "How can Shepherd benefit real estate investors?",
        a: "By leveraging AI, Shepherd helps investors make data-driven decisions, enhance property performance, and ultimately increase their income."
      },
      {
        q: "What types of products does Shepherd offer?",
        a: "Shepherd offers a range of solutions designed to optimize vacation rental income. From performance analytics to predictive modeling, our products empower investors to make informed choices."
