        a: "Absolutely! Whether you're a seasoned investor or just starting, Shepherd's user-friendly tools and insights cater to investors at every level of experience."
      },
      {
        q: "How do I get started with Shepherd?",
        a: "Getting started is easy. Simply sign up on our platform, and our team will guide you through the setup process to unleash the full potential of your vacation rental investments."
      },
      {
        q: "What kind of support does Shepherd provide?",
        a: "Shepherd offers dedicated customer support to assist you at every step. From onboarding to ongoing assistance, our team is committed to helping you achieve the best results with our AI-powered solutions."
      }
    ].each do |faq| %>
    <details class="group py-4 marker:content-['']">
      <summary class="flex w-full cursor-pointer select-none justify-between text-left text-base font-medium leading-7 text-zinc-900 group-open:text-primary-600 dark:group-open:text-primary-500 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden font-heading dark:text-zinc-100">
        <%= faq[:q] %>

        <svg class="ml-4 mt-0.5 h-6 w-6 flex-none stroke-zinc-700 dark:stroke-zinc-300 group-open:stroke-primary-500"
          fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M18 12H6"></path>
